        "TileImage": "$($repository 15551568-b1e2-4dd5-87d2-d394870617a9).Image",
        "Description": "Look at all these lovely (and disgusting) couples, 47 can&apos;t stand the sight of all this nauseating love.\r\rExcept for the targets, you must not hurt anyone else, not even the targets&apos; partners: imagine how much they will suffer when they are going to found out what happened to their significant other.\r\rExplosives might not be enough, try to look around, you may find what you actually need.\r\rGood hunting, 47.",
